<D>__{you get with it.}
<A>__{he sits down at his desk and begins going through his drawers, looking for something. she lowers the paper and looks over at him:}
<C>__{june }
<D>__{do you like my hair this way, or do you like it straight?}
<C>__{harry}
<D>__{it's very nice, sluggo. go hose out the kennel.}
