<D>__{get this first, will you.}
<A>__{she gets up and moves over to the desk:}
<C>__{june}
<D>__{they need people, because that hole is getting...}
<C>__{harry}
<P>__{(cutting her off)}
<D>__{remember, don't say i'm here 'til you find out who it is.}
<A>__{she picks up the receiver and speaks into it:}
<C>__{june}
<D>__{yeah?... i doubt that he's here at this present time... yeah, maybe later today sometime... who are you addressing? uh, the executive kennel maid... uh huh. yeah. okay, i will tell him... so long.}
